BOC Hong Kong to Raise Hong Kong Mortgage Rate, Hkej Reports

-- B y   S o p h i e   L e u n g
-- 
2011-09-17T01:15:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/boc-hong-kong-to-raise-hong-kong-mortgage-rate-hkej-reports.html
BOC  Hong Kong  (Holdings) Ltd. will
raise the mortgage rate linked to the Hong Kong interbank
offered rate on Sept. 19, the Hong Kong Economic Journal
reported today, citing the bank.  The mortgage rate will be increased by 20 basis points to
Hibor plus 2 percentage points to 2.5 percentage points,
according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sophie Leung in Hong Kong at 
 sleung59@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ryan Woo at 
 rwoo5@bloomberg.net  